<P><HI>BRISTOL:</HI> Printed by E. FARLEY and Co. for the AUTHOR: And &s;old in <HI>London</HI> by DODSLEY, in <HI>Pall-Mall</HI>; WALTERS, <HI>Charing-Cro&s;s</HI>; DA|VIES, in <HI>Ru&s;&s;el-&s;treet</HI>; KEARSLEY, on <HI>Ludgate-Hill</HI>; and ALMON, in <HI>Piccadilly</HI>; and by the BOOKSELLERS of <HI>Bri&s;tol</HI> and <HI>Bath.</HI></P>
